{"tid":1191630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失業潮將至？中國「搵工」搜尋量4月創新高","createTime":"2019-06-08T04:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:54:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91a1001499ae10d561cc561f7b137a30343a2f5f","tid":1191630,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190607/photo/bkn-20190607184133918-0607_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190607184710\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190607184133918-0607_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190607184710&h=7a5580b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國著名財經媒體彭博報道，貿易戰似乎已對中國就業市場造成衝擊！有內地主要搜尋引擎數據顯示，以「找工作」作為關鍵字的搜尋量，在4月飆至史上最高。<br />\n<br />\n作為經濟前瞻指標之一的中國5月官方製造業採購經理指數(PMI)跌至49.4，不僅低於盛衰分界線50，較4月更減少0.7。由此可見，就業市場確實有壓力。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，網上求職網站Zhaopin. com早於今年4月發布數據顯示，今年首3個月中國職位空缺與求職者的比例跌至1.68，大幅低於去年第4季的2.38及去年首季的1.91，為2015年初有紀錄以來最低。與去年第4季相比，職位空缺大跌7.6%，而求職人數則大升31%。<br />\n<br />\n更甚的是，目前若想在中國大城市工作，職位已「爭崩頭」，大約每兩名工人爭奪一個職位，即每份工作與每名工人的比例約0.51，較去年首季的0.71大幅下跌。Zhaopin當時更預期，最差的情況仍未出現，今年次季求職市場恐更趨緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190607/bkn-20190607184133918-0607_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190607%2Fbkn-20190607184133918-0607_00842_001.html&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW81T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=173d5cad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190607/bkn-20190607184133918-0607_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aaabf8e8c52461047d2e22e378d1b0067d9281e2","tid":1191630,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"之後到香港"},{"pid":"b469b94d1e3d1467af5969a359c88dc452dceff7","tid":1191630,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaabf8e8c52461047d2e22e378d1b0067d9281e2","tid":1191630,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"之後到香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"香港下半年失業率 會上升"},{"pid":"7f48bbbcf0aab1967a322cf2df19c3899f28ed52","tid":1191630,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來緊仲有畢業生"},{"pid":"538ba022acc5025894c4dcebdd157d965c4f5fcb","tid":1191630,"uid":58413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"經濟好多人轉工好正常。<br />\n刁帝千奇唔好放過班美國佬。"},{"pid":"6ead49c9a1a394e90581f456e39d36747400a7e6","tid":1191630,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f48bbbcf0aab1967a322cf2df19c3899f28ed52","tid":1191630,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來緊仲有畢業生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"850萬大學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}